OL,3,CPolice officers investigated over
OL,4,Chandling of Al Fayed complaints
OL,6,FA serving Metropolitan Police officer
OL,7,Fand four former officers are being
OL,8,Finvestigated over their handling of
OL,9,Fallegations of sexual abuse made
OL,10,Fagainst Mohamed Al Fayed, according to
OL,11,Freports.
OL,13,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,14,FConduct (IOPC) has launched a probe
OL,15,Finto the five for potential misconduct
OL,16,Ffollowing complaints against the
OL,17,Fformer Harrods owner, who died in 2023
OL,18,Faged 94.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
