CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778234501
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated over
OL,4,Chandling of Al Fayed complaints
OL,6,FMore than 400 allegations of sexual
OL,7,Fmisconduct have been made against Al
OL,8,FFayed dating back to 1977.
OL,10,FThe IOPC confirmed the investigation
OL,11,Finto the officers, which was launched
OL,12,Fin January 2025, related to reports
OL,13,Fmade against Al Fayed by four people.
OL,15,FIn a statement, the IOPC said: "The
OL,16,Finvestigation, which is being carried
OL,17,Fout by the Met's Directorate of
OL,18,FProfessional Standards under our
OL,19,Fdirection and control, involves
OL,20,Freports made by four victim-survivors.
OL,26,@wD@`OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778234501
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated over
OL,4,Chandling of Al Fayed complaints
OL,6,F"We began our directed investigation
OL,7,Fin January 2025.
OL,9,F"At this stage, five individuals, a
OL,10,Fserving Met officer and four former
OL,11,FMet officers, have been advised that
OL,12,Fthey are being investigated for
OL,13,Fpotential misconduct.
OL,15,F"At the end of our investigation, we
OL,16,Fwill decide whether any current or
OL,17,Fformer officers have, or would have
OL,18,Fhad if they were still serving, a
OL,19,Fdisciplinary case to answer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
