PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778234501
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated over
OL,4,Chandling of Al Fayed complaints
OL,6,F"The victims-survivors are being kept
OL,7,Fupdated on the progress of our
OL,8,Finvestigation."
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FA Met Police spokesperson said the
OL,16,Fforce was assisting the IOPC's
OL,17,Finvestigation into five officers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@OO]
