CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778234501
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated over
OL,4,Chandling of Al Fayed complaints
OL,6,FThe spokesperson said: "As part of
OL,7,Fthis, the IOPC is investigating
OL,8,Fcomplaints against five officers. One
OL,9,Fserving and four former officers are
OL,10,Fbeing investigated for potential
OL,11,Fmisconduct. The serving of notices
OL,12,Fdoes not mean that misconduct
OL,13,Fproceedings will necessarily follow.
OL,15,F"Our investigation into individuals
OL,16,Fwho may have facilitated or enabled
OL,17,Foffending by Mohamed Al Fayed remains
OL,18,Factive."
OL,26,@nD@XOUwD@AOUzD@HO]
