OL,3,CPolice officers investigated over
OL,4,Chandling of Al Fayed complaints
OL,6,FIn March the Metropolitan Police said
OL,7,Fa main in his 60s was interviewed
OL,8,Funder caution over allegations of
OL,9,Fhuman trafficking and facilitating
OL,10,Frape in connection with the
OL,11,Finvestigation into Al Fayed.
OL,13,FIt came after three women were quizzed
OL,14,Fby detectives between February 25 and
OL,15,FMarch 5, also on suspicion of aiding
OL,16,Fand abetting rape and sexual assault,
OL,17,Fassisting the commission of sexual
OL,18,Foffences and human trafficking for
OL,19,Fsexual exploitation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
