PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778234501
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated over
OL,4,Chandling of Al Fayed complaints
OL,6,FPolice said no arrests were made and
OL,7,Fthe investigation is ongoing.
OL,9,FThe Metropolitan Police previously
OL,10,Fannounced the force is investigating
OL,11,Findividuals surrounding Al Fayed who
OL,12,Fcould have enabled him to carry out
OL,13,Fmore than 400 sexual misconduct
OL,14,Fcrimes, which are claimed to have
OL,15,Fspanned decades between 1977 and 2014.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
